title: Billy Joel - Greatest Hits Vols. 1-2 (1973-1985) [V0](Big Papi)
description:
Big Papi usually combines multi-CD sets under 1 Album, but this set is an exception since Disc 1 is 1973-1977 and Disc 2 is 1978- 1985. Therefore, you will see 2 Albums in player view. If you want both discs under 1 Album view, edit the Album Title of both Discs to the same name and they will merge.

Also, some tracks are Studio and some are Live. Just another example of Record Companies trying to increase their profits by making us think we are buying something we are not. But....some of us like those one-off versions so let's be grateful for those special tracks.

- Big Papi
